	%p.day September 27th
	%h3 Day Four at Relevance
	%p
		Thursday was a good day. I paired with Michael again on another project. Kevin and I accomplished more wireframing. We understood the goals of the app a lot more. We focused on getting our ideas out so that when Kevin was away the next week, Michael would be able to pick up where we left off.
	%p
		After a busy day of thinking and disussion, we made plans to order pizza and chill at the office. We went out for a drink and called it a night. I started to come to the realization that it was my last night in Durham, but I had become attached to this amazing group of people.
	%p.notes
		%em Note 4:
		Need to figure out how to see these people that live so far away more often. Once a year will not be good enough.

